{"root":{"data":{"text":"软件工程"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件工程定义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi5guwn9s0","created":1775725490887,"text":"由方法、工具和过程三个部分组成"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi5oka3hc0","created":1775725507658,"text":"PDCA（Plan、Do、Check、Action）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"软件配置管理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"前期准备"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件配置管理和版本管理(CMM)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"记忆: 工程配置管理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"配置标识"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"配置检查"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"配置审计"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"配置状态跟踪"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"版本发布管理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"记录和报告配置项的变更, 可追踪和恢复版本"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"软件度量"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件工程量化"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"软件工程评估"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"能力成熟度模型CMM"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"能力成熟度模型集成CMMI"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件工程"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi6obiu6w0","created":1775725585493,"text":"软件开发方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi6s8pvqw0","created":1775725594031,"text":"形式化方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi6yv7iao0","created":1775725608451,"text":"净室软件工程CSE"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi76pvgi80","created":1775725625543,"text":"函数理论（记忆：玩一阵）","note":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi8c67cio0","created":1775725715778,"text":"完备性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8dqit2w0","created":1775725719184,"text":"一致性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8fh4se80","created":1775725722969,"text":"正确性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi7c5cwx40","created":1775725637363,"text":"抽样理论"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8lblx740","created":1775725735696,"text":"限制"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi8n3iio80","created":1775725739560,"text":"对工程师要求高"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8p6awrc0","created":1775725744082,"text":"不依赖传统单元测试不实际"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8w4921c0","created":1775725759196,"text":"属于传统软件工程体系，无法解决所有工程问题"},"children":[]}]}]}]